   At Nevo, the Team Lead is the key to how well we are able
   		to execute our projects.  They are responsible for architecture
   		and design decisions, for marshalling the technical team, and
   		for providing the level of technical insight and understanding
   		that makes the difference between an adequate project and a
   		truly superior one.

   <p>As a Team Lead you should have:

   <ul class="listText">
    	<li>At least five years of solid technical experience
   		</li><li>All the skills of an outstanding developer.
   		</li><li>Deep understanding of the technologies we use, and a passion
   				 to extend and expand that knowledge.
   		</li><li>Strong interpersonal skills.  You will need to command the
   				 respect of the technical team, and guide them as a player/coach.
   		</li><li>Experience with software engineering processes - unit testing,
   				 source control, continuous build, UML, documentation generation,
   				 are all examples.
   </ul>

